{
  "stem": "4345.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My family, I said, is already slaughtered.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, [GERMAN], I am still alive, and this is-- this is going to keep me alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as long as I live, I want them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he became very-- because I said no and he said yes, and I disobeyed, he started to pull-- it was a heavy rope, like-- like a-- like a rope, you know, and he started to pull, so I'm holding this rope like this, you know, not to ruin the pictures.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm resisting with all of my might, because he could cut into my neck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he couldn't do anything, so he takes off the-- his-- his rifle and he gives me a knock and I fall to the floor.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was bleeding profusely, and if I'm not mistaken-- he inflicted this on me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was opened up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I can't, there is nothing-- I-- I didn't want to do anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wanted to have this as my souvenir of what had happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He thought I was dead because, you know, he gave me a split, and I-- I just fell.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I found myself on top of the barrack with the other girls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had all dried-out blood on me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was all bloody and I had-- and-- and I felt for my pictures, and I had them on my neck.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, thank God.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said thank you, God, in Jewish, for this gift.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then they-- that-- that same day they gave us clothes, you know, the dresses already from dead people with the-- with the letter KL, konzentrationslager.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Big sizes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, they-- they-- this was an exterminating camp also, Flossenburg, where the crematoriums were there, you'll see it on the picture.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
